Deep prune functions.When you want to remove every extra properties that are not defined in the type including nested objects, you can use typia.misc.prune<T>() function. Also, if you want to perform type safe pruning, you can use typia.misc.isPrune<T>(), typia.misc.assertPrune<T>() or typia.misc.validatePrune<T>() functions instead.
